### mangleCoveragePath() {#a9dc80501043000f0bf75820ebfef69c4}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>static std::string mangleCoveragePath (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a> Filename, bool PreservePaths)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Convert a path to a gcov filename.

If PreservePaths is true, this translates &quot;/&quot; to &quot;#&quot;, &quot;..&quot; to &quot;^&quot;, and drops &quot;.&quot;, to match gcov.

Definition at line <a href="#l00639">639</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/profiledata/gcov-cpp">GCOV.cpp</a>.

<Link id="l00505" /><CodeLine lineNumber="505"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (v == &amp;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/gcovblock/#affc0977b112746478fa3a155d3c40ea6">succ</a>-&gt;dst)</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00566" /><CodeLine lineNumber="566"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   - Only output 0% or 100% if it&#39;s exactly that value</span></CodeLine>
